    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "At least one of the reasons seems to be that actors are literally \"cutting corners\" when the next cell on their path requires turning. Even actors that don't share cells (vehicles) don't move from cell center to cell center, but rather turn as soon as they enter a cell. I'm not just talking about corners of cells adjacent to their path, but even cells _on_ their path.\nThis behavior is clealy different from the original games and probably contributes a lot to this issue, it might even be the only problem here.\n"
  },
